1/2 27 1/2 36 5/8 39 3/8 +43.2% Amgen 49 1/2 38 1/4 44 3/4 53 3/8 +39.5 H.F. 
Ahmanson 19 5/8 16 7/8 19 7/8 21 7/8 +29.6 Warner-Lambert 67 1/2 61 7/8 70 3/4 
