<HEADLINE>
<P>
EAST VENTURA COUNTY FOCUS: OAK PARK; LIBRARY TO CLOSE FOR MAINTENANCE WORK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By TRACY WILSON 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Oak Park Library will be closed to the public Thursday for maintenance and 
cleaning work, library officials said. 
</P>
<P>
 "It's kind of an annual cleaning before school starts," Librarian Martha 
Gifford said. 
</P>
<P>
 The library is a shared facility with Oak Park High School. 
</P>
<P>
 School custodians will shampoo carpets and conduct general maintenance work, 
Gifford said. 
</P>
<P>
 The library, at 899 N. Kanan Road, will reopen at its regularly scheduled 
hours from 3 to 7 p.m. Aug. 22. The library generally operates Mondays through 
Thursdays. TRACY WILSON 
</P>
